fishNotes: Dead. Tag recovered in the pool.
Potentially moved upstream from where we thought it had died.
Incorrectly classified at tag 18, based on other data, this sighting was likely tag 19
Found tag at bottom of pool
Hard time in pool getting a high signal. Highest 186
Seemed like it was moving downstream as we were tracking and stopped in the woody debris.
Dead found under moss while looking for tag.
May be movng in pool. Signal changes. We do feel we should be able to see the fish, but do not.
Tag still hard to get above 190.
We did get a 190 when looking for the tag. Other than that odd signal strength, maybfish moving.
